@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 60

actor "Usuario" as U
cloud "Hyperliquid L1\n(WS + REST)" as HL
cloud "Servicio Webhook\n(HTTPS)" as SW

node "Host Docker" as HOST {

    rectangle "Red: fieldx-edge" as EDGE #E3F2FD {
        node "fieldx-app\n(Node 20 + Fastify)" as APP {
            artifact "dist/server.js"
            artifact "public/\n(SPA Vite)"
            artifact "dist/persistence/migrations/"
        }
    }

    rectangle "Red: fieldx-internal" as INT #FFF3E0 {
        database "fieldx-postgres\n(PostgreSQL 16 + pgcrypto)" as PG
    }

    folder "Volúmenes" as VOLS #ECEFF1 {
        artifact "fieldx-postgres-data" as VPG
    }
}

U  --> APP : HTTP :3001\n(REST + WS + SPA)
APP --> PG : TCP 5432
APP --> HL : WS + REST  (saliente)
APP --> SW : HTTPS POST (saliente)

PG ..> VPG : datos persistentes

note right of APP
  Único proceso del backend.
  Sirve el SPA con
  @fastify/static desde /public.
  Composition root cablea
  servicios, adaptadores y
  workers.
end note

note bottom of PG
  Tablas: entidades, direcciones,
  alertas, notificaciones, lb_trades.
  Extensión pgcrypto cargada
  por la migración inicial.
end note

note bottom of HOST
  restart: unless-stopped.
  Healthchecks por servicio:
   - postgres: pg_isready
   - app: GET /health
  Arranque ordenado: app espera
  a postgres healthy.
end note

@enduml
